This paper is primarily focused on natural language processing (NLP) and the use of deep learning techniques to improve NLP systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of deep recurrent networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of word embeddings, which is a common technique in NLP and falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper discusses the potential applications of this technique in image captioning, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV).
